    Update["<b>update</b><br/>Msg → Model → (Model, Cmd Msg)"]

    Model["<b>Model</b><br/>route · events · categories<br/>cocktailCache · dialogs · ..."]

    Cmd["Cmd Msg<br/>(Http.get · Nav.pushUrl<br/>File.download · ...)"]

    View["<b>view</b><br/>Model → Html Msg"]

    DOM["HTML / SVG<br/>im Browser"]

    TheCocktailDB["TheCocktailDB API"]

    Browser -->|"user event"| Msg
    HTTP --> Msg
    Msg --> Update
    Update --> Model
    Update --> Cmd
    Model --> View
    View --> DOM
    DOM -->|"click / input"| Browser
    Cmd --> TheCocktailDB
    TheCocktailDB --> HTTP

